# Supabase Configuration for Direct Frontend Integration
# Get these values from: https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/api
# For production, use GitHub Secrets and Environment Variables

# Note: Use GitHub Secrets for sensitive keys!
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL should be set in GitHub Secrets
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY should be set in GitHub Secrets
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY should be set in GitHub Secrets (for server-side only)